            "title": "比亞迪利潤降幅超預期 受激烈競爭與監管趨嚴拖累",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"比亞迪利潤降幅超預期 受激烈競爭與監管趨嚴拖累\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/GnZe40bAlwUp_b8rXHigCg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-03/0830b580-2a56-11f1-bff3-91476397fd66\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">比亞迪利潤降幅超預期 受激烈競爭與監管趨嚴拖累</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
